reviewText: Great Tv series plenty of action and a good story line I would recommend this Tv series especially if you like Special Ops  or Cop type movies

2 reasons for purchasing: I transport myself to Hawaii and enjoy seeing places I have been.  I would live there but do not want to fly my aging horses or my min donkeys over. second reason: eye candy: Hawaii and  Steve and Chin. excellent what directors can accomplish in 1 hour!!
One of my favorite TV shows is Hawaii Five-O. The product was wonderful except the fifth season was not in the box like the other four.
Love this show, use to watch the old Five O this one over the top even better
